amount of light going through.

00:18:54.440 --> 00:18:57.260
And if we triple, we're going
to reduce it by a third.

00:18:57.260 --> 00:19:00.000
And if we quadruple, we're
going to reduce it by a fourth.

00:19:00.000 --> 00:19:02.316
And let's see if the
hypothesis is correct.

00:19:02.316 --> 00:19:03.250
It's not.

00:19:03.250 --> 00:19:05.220
But we're going to test it.

00:19:05.220 --> 00:19:08.475
And it's a logical
thing you might assume.

00:19:08.475 --> 00:19:10.350
And then we'll walk
through a derivation that

00:19:10.350 --> 00:19:12.972
