00:21:04.230 --> 00:21:05.570
Look at that.

00:21:05.570 --> 00:21:08.060
What sort of curve is it?

00:21:08.060 --> 00:21:09.150
Exponential.

00:21:09.150 --> 00:21:10.975
It looks like one at least.

00:21:10.975 --> 00:21:12.850
And we can test whether
