00:30:38.330 --> 00:30:41.050
And then we would take
the log of both sides,

00:30:41.050 --> 00:30:45.410
typically, and solve for
our l based on the alphas

00:30:45.410 --> 00:30:46.460
that we have here.

00:30:46.460 --> 00:30:49.270
Again, units of alpha would
